The plot:

Taking Arash car as payment for his dads heroin addiction,drug dealing pimp Saeed runs into a mysterious women walking the streets of Bad City at night.Taking the women back to his apartment,Saeed discovers that she is actually a vampire,who reveals her fangs and kills him.As the women walks out of the apartment,Arash goes to try and pay Saeed for the car,only to discover that Saeed has been killed by the girl who walks home alone at night.

